<h2>Viewvc link to line number</h2>
I am always emailing a link to a change-set or code-comment or code-section. The thing I always forget how to do is to link to the code line number in viewvc.

So without further ado.

<code>
Use the query-string:</code>

?view=markup#l&lt;line-number&gt;

i.e.:

http://svn.collab.net/viewvc/svn/trunk/README?view=markup#l30
